"5 teaspoons olive oil, divided","4 cups thinly sliced red onion","1 1/2 teaspoons chopped fresh thyme","1/2 cup cabernet sauvignon or other dry red wine","2 tablespoons balsamic vinegar","3/4 teaspoon salt, divided","1  (8-ounce) package sliced mushrooms","1 1/2 pounds ground sirloin","  Cooking spray","1/3 cup light mayonnaise","1 ounce blue cheese, crumbled (about 1/4 cup)","1  garlic clove, minced","6  (1 1/2-ounce) whole-wheat hamburger buns","1 1/2 cups baby arugula"